org.fhaes.neofhchart

Class FireChartSVG

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fhaes.neofhchart.FireChartSVG

  • public class FireChartSVG
extends java.lang.Object
    FireChartSVG Class. Graphs a fire history chart as an svg using FHUtil's AbstractFireHistoryReader.
    Author:
    Aaron Decker, Michael Ababio, Zachariah Ferree, Matthew Willie, Peter Brewer
